ener\">this place<\/a>&#xA0;being the best.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1.jpg\" alt=\"puerto viejo best things to do punta uva beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"puerto viejo best things to do punta uva beach\" class=\"wp-image-76073 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.sa