-whale-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Book your whale watching tour online<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-hotels-near-marino-ballena-national-park-uvita\">Hotels near Marino Ballena National Park, Uvita<\/h4>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/bungalows-ballena\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Bungalows Ballena\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14085548\/158567647-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Bungalows Ballena<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/casa-mediterranea\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Casa Mediterr&#xE1;nea\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14085954\/163198260-450x338.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Casa Mediterr&#xE1;nea<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<ul><li><strong>Season:<\/strong> January &#x2013; March OR July &#x2013; October for whale watching. The driest months are late November &#x2013; April.<\/li><li><strong>Crowds:<\/strong> Quiet. Making up a huge area of the national park, you might not see anyone on the beach all day! Be aware that at the weekends it can be busier.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201958\/uvita-8.jpg\" alt=\"best beaches uvita costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"240\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best beaches uvita costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-72351 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1363px) 100vw, 1363px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201958\/uvita-8.jpg 1363w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201958\/uvita-8-426x600.jpg 426w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201958\/uvita-8-575x810.jpg 575w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201958\/uvita-8-240x338.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201958\/uvita-8-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201958\/uvita-8-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201958\/uvita-8-128x180.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201958\/uvita-