l (15 minutes), you&#x2019;ll also find the beautiful <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/1FvvuE4rGvXQNwsi9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Playa Linda<\/a>. Situated off a dirt track, this beach is incredibly remote, meaning that you&#x2019;ll find very few people on your arrival. Playa Linda is also super long, eventually joining with Playa Matapalo to form one endless long stretch of beach along the coastline. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163446\/uvita-18.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-72542 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163446\/uvita-18.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163446\/uvita-18-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163446\/uvita-18-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163446\/uvita-18-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163446\/uvita-18-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163446\/uvita-18-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163446\/uvita-18-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163446\/uvita-18-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163446\/uvita-18-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163446\/uvita-18-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/20