itself. One of these beaches is Espadilla Sur, a pristine white sand beach where iguanas roam freely, and the sounds of monkeys can be heard from the bordering forest. It&#x2019;s the perfect place to take a refreshing swim after your 20-minute hike through the park.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05.jpg\" alt=\"Manuel Antonio Beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"246\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Manuel Antonio Beach\" class=\"wp-image-72962 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1399px) 100vw, 1399px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05.jpg 1399w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-437x600.jpg 437w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-590x810.jpg 590w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-246x338.jpg 246w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-119x163.jpg 119w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-131x180.jpg 131w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-560x768.jpg 560w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-746x1024.jpg 746w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-787x1080.jpg 787w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-1049x1440.jpg 1049w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-300x412.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-600x823.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-22x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Entrance fee:<\/strong> 18-19 USD a ticket for a self-guided tour through the national park. You can <a href=\"https:\/\/serviciosenlinea.sinac.go.cr\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">buy tickets here<\/a>, although you&#x2019;ll have to register before purchase. It&#x2019;s worth buying a ticket just to spend the day on one of the best beaches in Costa Rica!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-hotels-near-espadilla-sur-beach-manuel-antonio\">Hotels near Espadilla Sur Beach, Manuel Antonio<\/h4>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"h