sta-rica\/manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Manuel Antonio<\/a> are the <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/QGV3NjHt7Vvt3x1L9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Esterillos beaches<\/a>, a collection of beaches (east, west, and central) that make up one long stretch of brown sand. The dark color of the sand is beautifully complemented by the bold green forest and the deep blue ocean surrounding it. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/13132252\/beaches-costa-rica-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-79799 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/13132252\/beaches-costa-rica-2.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/13132252\/beaches-costa-rica-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/13132252\/beaches-costa-rica-2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/13132252\/beaches-costa-rica-2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/13132252\/beaches-costa-rica-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/13132252\/beaches-costa-rica-2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/13132252\/beaches-costa-rica-2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/13132252\/beaches-costa-rica-2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/13132252\/beaches-costa-rica-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.c