r\">\n<ul><li><strong>Season:<\/strong> Year-round surf, but the driest months are December &#x2013; April.<\/li><li><strong>Crowds:<\/strong> Quiet as it&#x2019;s a little harder to get to than the other Santa Teresa beaches<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27182814\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-28.jpg\" alt=\"santa teresa things to do Mal Pais Tide Pools\"><\/noscript><img width=\"247\" height=\"338\" alt=\"santa teresa things to do Mal Pais Tide Pools\" class=\"wp-image-74802 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1403px) 100vw, 1403px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27182814\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-28.jpg 1403w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27182814\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-28-438x600.jpg 438w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27182814\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-28-592x810.jpg 592w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27182814\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-28-247x338.jpg 247w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27182814\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-28-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27182814\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-28-119x163.jpg 119w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27182814\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-28-132x180.jpg 132w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27182814\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-28-561x768.jpg 561w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27182814\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-28-748x1024.jpg 748w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27182814\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-28-789x1080.jpg 789w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploa