019;re not advanced, it&#x2019;s a fun place to come and watch the surfers paddle out and catch their waves&#x2014;a real show of skill! As it&#x2019;s a little out of town, it&#x2019;s more scenic and less busy than the main Santa Teresa beaches.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Better to watch surfing, rather than swim, as there are powerful currents and many rocks.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26034507\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-7.jpg\" alt=\"santa teresa playa carmen\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"santa teresa playa carmen\" class=\"wp-image-74657 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26034507\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-7.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26034507\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-7-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26034507\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-7-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26034507\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-7-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26034507\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-7-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26034507\/sant